--- !u!114 &583321360
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 583321358}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c5822b04acff06c449bfc5e946edd93b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CutsceneManager2
  textComponent: {fileID: 676889352}
  lines:
  - One day in the forest, Sang Kancil finds himself craving for some berries. So
    he decides to wander the forest in search for some
  - Little did he know, something else was closely following him.
  - '"Oh! some berries just what I was looking for" says Sang Kancil'
  - "While Sang Kancil was eating. The mysterious figure crawled closer and closer
    behind him until\u2026"
  - '*SNAP*'
  - Sang Kancil turns to see what made that sound. As he does, he sees that the mysterious
    figure was none other than Sang Harimau.
  - '"Oh! Good morning Sang Harimau." greets Sang Kancil'
  - '"Well, good morning to you too, Sang Kancil. Having breakfast?" Sang Harimau
    responds'
  - '"Yes, I am. In fact, I was just finishing up, so I should probably get going
    now." says Sang Kancil'
  - "\"I\u2019m afraid I can\u2019t let you do that, Sang Kancil. You see, I was
    also looking to eat breakfast.\" Sang Harimau states"
  - "\"And seeing as I am the king of the forest, I\u2019ve decided that it shall
    be you.\""
  - "\"Is that so? Well you\u2019ll have to catch me first!\" Sang Kancil says as
    he runs"
  - "After running so much, Sang Kancil starts breathing heavily \"Hah\u2026hah\""
  - '"Nowhere to run now, Kancil" Sang Harimau teases'
  - As Sang Harimau gets closer to Sang Kancil, he starts thinking about to get out
    of this situation. He glances at the river nearby and suddenly, he gets an idea
  - "\"You\u2019re strength and speed are truly great, Sang Harimau. However, they\u2019re
    no match for my king.\" says Sang Kancil"
  - '"Your king? There is no other king in this forest other than I." questions Sang
    Harimau'
  - "\"If you don\u2019t believe me, you just need to look into that river.\" says
    Sang Kancil as he points to the river. "
  - Sang Harimau goes to the river and stares at his reflection. As he stares, he
    starts growling at the reflection
  - Then, Sang Harimau claws at the reflection.
  - Finally, Sang Harimau decides to pounce on the river
  - When he realizes what had happened, Sang Kancil was already gone.
  - '"CURSE YOU SANG KANCIL!"'
  - 
  textSpeed: 0.05
  introCutsceneComponent: {fileID: 865040270}
  introCutsceneFrame: {fileID: 865040268}
  endingCutsceneComponent: {fileID: 1008975355}
  endingCutsceneFrame: {fileID: 1008975353}
